name: Pac-Man World 3 [NDS]
description:
Pac-Man World 3 is an arcade game developed by NAMCO and Blitz Games. It was originally released in 2005. Bandai Namco Entertainment published the game. Most rawgers rated the game as "Meh".
You can play Pac-Man World 3 on Xbox, Nintendo DS, GameCube and PlayStation 2.
